thread.title_full: Doheny's Pool Supplies Fast reviewed by Caryl Smith Huiras

author: Caryl Smith Huiras
title: Caryl Smith Huiras
text:
This company does what it says....I ordered 50 lbs of pills and shock for my pool. I almost went locally (at a higher price) to have them now. Doheny said I would have them next day. So I took a gamble, they were on my porch by 2:00 pm.
Thank you, Doheny, you are our go to company from now on!!!
